gal  JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON s.bestObjID=gal.objID and s.specObjID=gal.specObjID  JOIN PhotoZ as z ON z.objID=gal.objID WHERE  gal.ra BETWEEN # and #  AND gal.dec BETWEEN # and #  AND gal.mode=#  AND gal.type=#  AND gal.petroRad_u># and gal.petroRad_g># and gal.petroRad_r># and gal.petroRad_i># and gal.petroRad_z># and gal.petroRadErr_g>#  AND gal.petroMag_g BETWEEN # and #  AND s.z BETWEEN # and #  AND (dbo.fSourceType(s.sourceType)=# or dbo.fSourceType(s.sourceType)=#) ORDER BY  gal.objID
